com.impossibl.stencil.engine.parsing

Class StencilParserBaseVisitor<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T>
      • com.impossibl.stencil.engine.parsing.StencilParserBaseVisitor<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The return type of the visit operation. Use Void for operations with no return type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    StencilParserVisitor<T>, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>

    public class StencilParserBaseVisitor<T>
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T>
implements StencilParserVisitor<T>
    This class provides an empty implementation of StencilParserVisitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
